Package: scclust
Type: Package
Title: Size-Constrained Clustering
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2017-03-23
Authors@R: c(
    person("Fredrik", "Savje", email = "fredrik.savje@berkeley.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Jasjeet", "Sekhon", role = "aut"))
Description:
    Provides functions for computationally efficient size-constrained clustering
    with near-optimal performance. The package wraps for the `scclust` C library.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.3),
    distances
Imports:
Suggests:
    testthat
NeedsCompilation: yes
